OL,5, A train driver crashed into the buffers
OL,6, at a station shortly after sending a   
OL,7, Whatsapp message about the death of    
OL,8, Formula 1 commentator Murray Walker.   
OL,10,FThe Merseyrail train was travelling at 
OL,11,F40mph (64km/h) instead of 15mph        
OL,12,F(24km/h) when the cab derailed at      
OL,13,FKirkby station on 13 March 2021.       
OL,15,FAt Liverpool Crown Court, 59-year-old  
OL,16,FPhillip Hollis admitted endangering    
OL,17,Fpassengers' safety.                    
OL,19,FHe was handed a 12-month prison        
OL,20,Fsentence, suspended for two years.     
